    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a project car or a source for parts. The engine has significant performance issues and requires a major overhaul, and the transmission shifts roughly. Externally, there is noticeable body damage, including several large dents and areas of rust, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear with torn upholstery. It is currently not recommended for daily use without substantial mechanical work.",
