      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp with an 8,000 RPM redline. This example boasts a pristine subframe, with comprehensive preventative maintenance including a Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul and WPC-treated rod bearings. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by a factory-spec variable M differential lock and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, this vehicle retains its original factory tolerances and mechanical integrity, offering a pure, naturally aspirated driving experience with zero deferred maintenance.",
